01:10:37.055 --> 01:10:38.421
I'm... I'm very tired.

01:10:38.423 --> 01:10:40.023
Yes! Okay? Yes!

01:10:40.025 --> 01:10:41.424
And if you even think

01:10:41.426 --> 01:10:43.860
about coming back here
to see me,

01:10:43.862 --> 01:10:45.161
